{"tid":542404,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸男咬電池辨真假 一咬即在嘴邊爆炸","createTime":"2018-01-27T12:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T14:27:50.000Z","uid":137840,"like":132,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"66d9ff56987937256ed09d9109e9f0c3391b3d9f","tid":542404,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"大陸山寨假貨很多，消費者購物時都份外小心，擔心購買到假貨。大陸南京一名男子在電腦商場想為 iPhone 更換電池，擔心店家提供的電池有問題，於是想到特別的方法去驗貨。這位男士可能以為電池和黃金一樣，於是決定用牙咬去判別電池真偽，結果就成為國際趣聞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/202600_34972c28ff00e9ec87755eda3addad84.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F202600_34972c28ff00e9ec87755eda3addad84.png&h=a5ab3255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當男子拿起電池一咬，竟然破壞了鋰電池的結構，電池馬上起火爆炸。從閉路電視拍攝到的影像，電池爆炸時在空中出現一個火球，幸好爆炸時電池已經離開男子的嘴巴，否則後果可以非常嚴重。現時無法得知男士咬的電池是 Apple 原廠還是山寨假貨，如果擔心店家更換的電池是假貨，最佳的方法還是到 Apple Store 或官方認可的維修商更換。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NuTWg7TqVt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNuTWg7TqVt8&d=UMA%2FSFSLGIuJQGbdLu604V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=654f296a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NuTWg7TqVt8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NuTWg7TqVt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNuTWg7TqVt8&d=UMA%2FSFSLGIuJQGbdLu604V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=654f296a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NuTWg7TqVt8</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/26/china-guy-bite-on-iphone-battery-got-exploded-right-away/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2Fchina-guy-bite-on-iphone-battery-got-exploded-right-away%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=UMA%2FSFSLGIuJQGbdLu604V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2